OL,3,CScotland's World Cup hopes knocked
OL,4,Cafter Japan and Sweden draw 1-1
OL,6,FScotland's chances of progressing to
OL,7,Fthe knockout stages of the World Cup
OL,8,Fare looking even more distant after a
OL,9,F1-1 draw between Sweden and Japan on
OL,10,FThursday night.
OL,12,FBoth Graham Potter and Hajime
OL,13,FMoriyasu's teams will have been
OL,14,Fpleased by the result, with Japan
OL,15,Ffinishing second place in Group F and
OL,16,FSweden top of the third place teams,
OL,17,Fthe best eight of whom can still go
OL,18,Fthrough.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
