OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782478095
OL,3,CScotland's World Cup hopes knocked
OL,4,Cafter Japan and Sweden draw 1-1
OL,6,FHowever Scotland was hoping for Sweden
OL,7,Fto lose by four or more goals to Japan
OL,8,Fin order to boost Steve Clarke's
OL,9,Fteam's chances of progressing to the
OL,10,Fnext stage of the World Cup.
OL,12,FEcuador's 2-1 victory against Germany
OL,13,Ffurther dented Scotland's hopes of
OL,14,Fmaking it through to the last 32.
OL,16,FScotland are now in third place of
OL,17,FGroup C, meaning their only chances of
OL,18,Fmaking it through will be to become
OL,19,Fone of the top eight of 12 third-
OL,20,Fplaced sides, with more matches yet to
OL,21,Fbe played before this is decided.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
