OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782478095
OL,3,CScotland's World Cup hopes knocked
OL,4,Cafter Japan and Sweden draw 1-1
OL,6,FAmong the third placed teams, Scotland
OL,7,Fare eighth, with three points and a
OL,8,Fgoal difference of -3, and below them
OL,9,Fare the likes of Senegal, who play
OL,10,FIraq from 8pm today, and Belgium, who
OL,11,Fkick-off against New Zealand tomorrow
OL,12,Fat 4am.
OL,14,FThis makes Scotland's chances of
OL,15,Fprogressing to the next stage of their
OL,16,Ffirst World Cup since 1998
OL,17,Fincreasingly fainter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
