OL,3,CScotland's World Cup hopes knocked
OL,4,Cafter Japan and Sweden draw 1-1
OL,6,FFollowing Scotland's disappointing 3-1
OL,7,Fdefeat to Brazil in Wednesday, many
OL,8,Floyal followers who had travelled to
OL,9,FAmerica said they were facing a
OL,10,F"special kind of torture" as they
OL,11,Fremained stuck in limbo.
OL,13,FChris Findlay, 66, travelled to Miami
OL,14,Ffrom his home city of Edinburgh.
OL,16,FHe said: "It's a special kind of
OL,17,Ftorture. We have to watch one game
OL,18,Fafter another, kind of hoping for
OL,19,Fperhaps an unlikely result, and yeah,
OL,20,Fbut it's where we are.
OL,26,@xD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782478095
OL,3,CScotland's World Cup hopes knocked
OL,4,Cafter Japan and Sweden draw 1-1
OL,6,F"It's, I guess, better than being
OL,7,Fcompletely out. There's still a
OL,8,Fchance, and we just have to get our
OL,9,Ffingers crossed, other results square
OL,10,Faway."
OL,12,FJohn Linstead, 72, added: "We came
OL,13,Fdown from Boston, and we have a
OL,14,Fbeautiful hotel here in Miami. We're
OL,15,Fgoing out on Saturday morning, but we
OL,16,Fleft an open book to where we want to
OL,17,Fgo next.
OL,19,F"It could be a Mexico, or New Jersey,
OL,20,For New York, or Houston. We're just in
OL,21,Flimbo.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@FO]tD@[OU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782478095
OL,3,CScotland's World Cup hopes knocked
OL,4,Cafter Japan and Sweden draw 1-1
OL,6,F"We want to know before we cancel
OL,7,Fflights and book an early room, we
OL,8,Fjust sort of want to finish to get our
OL,9,Fplans finalised to make it work.
OL,11,F"We want to stay, and we're hoping,
OL,12,Fand we want to go to full run. Go to
OL,13,Fyour next show for the first time, see
OL,14,FScotland ever.
OL,16,F"That's why I brought my son here,
OL,17,Fbecause this is the third world cup
OL,18,FI've been to, and I've never seen
OL,19,FScotland go into the third, so we're
OL,20,Fgonna do it this time, hopefully it
OL,21,Fwill do, it'll work for us, I hope."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU}D@dO]
